{"questionId":"12307","questionHtml":"<p>Test this claim at the 5% level of significance.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>H<sub>0</sub>: The sequence contains equal numbers of each digit.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(A1) </strong></em></p>\n<p>H<sub>1</sub>: The sequence does not contain equal numbers of each digit.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\chi _{{\\text{calc}}}^2 = \\frac{{\\left( {9 + 1 + 25 + 1 + 25 + 49 + 1 + 9 + 4 + 16} \\right)}}{{20}} = 7\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <msubsup> <mi>χ</mi> <mrow> <mrow> <mtext>calc</mtext> </mrow> </mrow> <mn>2</mn> </msubsup> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mrow> <mo>(</mo> <mrow> <mn>9</mn> <mo>+</mo> <mn>1</mn> <mo>+</mo> <mn>25</mn> <mo>+</mo> <mn>1</mn> <mo>+</mo> <mn>25</mn> <mo>+</mo> <mn>49</mn> <mo>+</mo> <mn>1</mn> <mo>+</mo> <mn>9</mn> <mo>+</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mo>+</mo> <mn>16</mn> </mrow> <mo>)</mo> </mrow> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>20</mn> </mrow> </mfrac> <mo>=</mo> <mn>7</mn> </math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>The number of degrees of freedom is 9.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\chi _{0.95{\\text{;}}\\,\\,5}^2 = 16.919\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <msubsup> <mi>χ</mi> <mrow> <mn>0.95</mn> <mrow> <mtext>;</mtext> </mrow> <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace> <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace> <mn>5</mn> </mrow> <mn>2</mn> </msubsup> <mo>=</mo> <mn>16.919</mn> </math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\chi _{{\\text{calc}}}^2 < 16.919\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <msubsup> <mi>χ</mi> <mrow> <mrow> <mtext>calc</mtext> </mrow> </mrow> <mn>2</mn> </msubsup> <mo>&lt;</mo> <mn>16.919</mn> </math></span>.&nbsp;Hence H<sub>0</sub> is accepted.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[7 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"12307","referenceCode":"EXM.1.SL.TZ0.11a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Test this claim at the 5% level of significance.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 7]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","SL 4.11—Expected, observed, hypotheses, chi squared, gof, t-test"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}